License boundary note for PHD maintainers:

Everything inside skills/surface/ is governed by CC BY-NC 4.0. Because PHD
bundles this directory, the PHD distribution as a whole is non-commercial
(see the repository-root NOTICE.md). The rest of PHD's glue code (commands,
templates, hooks, agents outside surface, the code-minimalism skill) is MIT.
To obtain a fully-MIT, commercial-friendly build, remove skills/surface/
entirely and drop the /phd:probe, /phd:review, and /phd:defend commands that
depend on it.
